             was indicted for <rs id="t18040411-67-off399" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18040411-67-off399" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18040411-67-off399" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18040411-67-cd400" type="crimeDate">22d of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18040411-67-off399 t18040411-67-cd400"></join>, a cloth great coat, value 20 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18040411-67-victim719" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Lindsay
                  <interp inst="t18040411-67-victim719" type="surname" value="Lindsay"></interp>
